	<p pid="a.45.2/1">Live pilot testing of the national firearms licensing management system started in two forces on <phrase class="date" code="2006-06-05">5 June</phrase>. If this is successful, it will be rolled out to all forces over the following seven to nine months.</p>
</reply>
